\c 8
\s Amosi anoratidzwa tswanda ine zvibereko
\p
\v 1 Hezvi zvandakaratidzwa naIshe Jehovha, tarirai, tswanda inezvibereko
\p zvezhizha.
\v 2 Akati, "Amosi, unooneiko?"
\s Ini ndikati, "Tswanda inezvibereko zvezhizha." Zvino Jehovha akati kwandiri,
\p "Kuguma kwasvikira vanhu vangu vaIsiraeri, handichatongovadarikizve.
\v 3 Nziyo
\s dzetemberi dzichashanduka kuungudza
\s nezuva iro," ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe Jehovha; zvitunha zvichavapo zvizhinji,
\s vachazvikandira kunze kwose vanyerere.
\p
\v 4 Inzwai chinhu ichi, iyemi, munoda
\s kumedza vanoshaiwa, nokuparadza varombo venyika, S muchiti, "Kugara kwo
\s mwedzi kuchapfuura riniko, kuti titengese zviyo? Uye Sabata, kuti tizarure
\s matura ezviyo? Tichatapudza efa, nokukurisa shekeri, tichinyengera nezviyero
\p zvinonyengera;
\v 6 kuti titenge varombonesirivha, navanoshaiwa tichipiwa shangu mbiri, tichitengesa makoto ezviyo?"
\p
\v 7 Jehovha akapika noukuru hwaJakobho, achiti, "Zvirokwazvo, handingatongokanganwi rimwe ramabasa avo nokusingaperi.
\v 8 Ko nyika haingadederi pamusoro pechinhu ichi, mumwe nomumwe agerepo haangachemi here? Zvirokwazvo, ichakwira yose soRwizi, ichatutuma ndokudererazve, soRwizi, rwebipiti.
\v 9 Zvino nezuva iro ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe Jehovha ndichavirisa zuva masikati makuru, ndichaisa rima panyika achiri masikati.
\v 10 Ndichashandura mitambo yenyu kuve kuchema, nenziyo dzenyu dzose kuve kurira kwokuchema; ndichafukidza zviuno zvose masaga, nokuita misoro yose mhazha; ndichazviita sapanochemwa mwanakomana akazvarwa ari mumwechete, nokuguma kwazvo sezuva rakaipa kwazvo.
\p
\v 11 "Tarirai, mazuva anouya ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe Jehovha andichatuma nzara panyika, isati iri nzara yezvokudya, kana nyota yemvura, asi yokunzwa mashoko aJehovha.
\v 12 Vachadzungaira vachibva kugungwa vachienda kugungwa, vachibva kumusoro vachienda mabvazuva; vachamhanya pose-pose vachitsvaka shoko raJehovha, asi havangariwani.
\v 13 Nezuva iro mhandara dzakanaka namajaya vachaziya nenyota.
\v 14 Vanopika vezvivi zveSamaria, vachiti, `Namwari wako mupenyu, iwe Dhani; uye, Nenzira yeBheerishebha mhenyu, ivo vachawira pasi, vakasazomukazve.' "
